data.description: ***Foundation, drywall to be repaired prior to closing and hall bath flooring to be replaced before closing!*** This is your chance to own a great home centrally located in SW Fort Worth with an open floorplan, 2 living or dining areas and a huge backyard! Mature trees line the streets of the neighborhood creating a great ambiance pulling into your new home!  If you'd like to finance in add'l renovations or updates, you can use a 203k FHA loan or a conventional HomeStyle loan to renovate within your loan which means LESS OUT OF POCKET for you! Be sure to ask your agent about down payment assistance loan programs as well as the mortgage credit programs where you could be purchasing a home for very little down! ***PRICED WELL UNDER NEARBY HOMES FOR NEEDED TLC***
